<header>
    <%- include("../partials/header.ejs")%>
 </header>

<body>
 <h1>Feedback Form</h1>
 <p> Please let us know if you have any questions <br> or comments about our website so far! </p>
 <form method="GET" action="mailto:purdue.epics.isd.track@gmail.com" enctype="text/plain">
    <div>Subject</div>
    <input type="text" name="subject">

    <div>Message</div>
    <textarea name="body"></textarea>

    <br/>
    <input type="submit" value="">
</form>

</body>
<p align="left"> Some stuff we're currently working on in case you're wondering and want to message about it: </p>
<ul>
	<li> Being able to edit student's profiles</li>
	<li> Being able to extract the data for the goals into an excel sheet </li>
	<li> Displaying graphs of data for visual representation </li>
	<li> Student/Parent Portal to view goal progress</li>
</ul>
<script>
$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#bt1').click(function() {
        $('#fr1').attr('action',
                       'mailto:purdue.epics.isd.track@gmail.com?subject=' +
                       $('#tb1').val() + '&body=' + $('#tb2').val());
        $('#fr1').submit();
    });
});
</script>

